{"metadata":{"title":"setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)PushwooshConfig(cm)setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets additional notification authorization options beyond the SDK defaults.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PushwooshConfig"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setAdditionalAuthorizationOptions:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@E@UNAuthorizationOptions","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UNAuthorizationOptions"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"options"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"options","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The additional ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNAuthorizationOptions"},{"text":" to request.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When calling ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"registerForPushNotifications"},{"text":", the SDK requests these permissions by default:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"UNAuthorizationOptionBadge","typ